      "text": [
        " أَبُو اَلْحَسَنِ اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «يَنْبَغِي لِلرَّجُلِ أَنْ يُوَسِّعَ عَلَى عِيَالِهِ لِئَلاَّ يَتَمَنَّوْا مَوْتَهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1742 - Abu Al-Hasan Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) said:\n\"A man ought to provide generously for his family so that they do not wish for his death.\""
        ]
      }
